snippet.title: Jurassic World Evolution 2: Dominion Biosyn Expansion | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Discover the biggest expansion yet with the Jurassic World Evolution 2: Dominion Biosyn Expansion. Experience a completely new and immersive campaign focused on the events of Biosyn Sanctuary from Universal Pictures and Amblin Entertainment’s Jurassic World Dominion.

Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1966010/Jurassic_World_Evolution_2_Dominon_Biosyn_Expansion

Immerse yourself in a thrilling new campaign that expands on the Jurassic World Dominion story. Play through a gripping new ‘what if’ scenario based on the epic events from the film. Construct a range of new buildings tied to the campaign, experience innovative new gameplay mechanics, and engage with an array of all-new prehistoric species. Encounter highly requested feathered dinosaurs, plus additional cosmetic variants and skins for existing species.

For more news and information about Jurassic World Evolution 2: 
Website: www.jurassicworldevolution2.com 
Facebook: facebook.com/JurassicWorldEvolution 
Twitter: www.twitter.com/JW_Evolution 
Instagram: @jurassicworldevolution
